entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Incoming fighter vessels. Scans show weapons armed. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrived_at_loc: \#pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Arrived at rendezvous. Wait here for Transport to arrive. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.abort: Gee, thanks. I'll find my own way back, thank you very much!
